pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\export.sh:cp -r $SRCDIR/batch/exportproductdataforpharmacyportals/*.option $DESTDIR/proc/
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_global.vars:export MARATHON_LOG_CONFIGDIR=$INI_PATH   # export important for framework log4cplusplus
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_global.vars:export MARATHON_LOG_LOGSDIR=$LOG_PATH 	# export important for framework log4cplusplus
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: #Purpose:			starts, stops and status the exemplar binary zdpdruckuiserv_at for presentation only
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: readonly LIBRARY_PATH=${LIB_PATH}/servclnt/01.18.01.06/sharedlib/release
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: readonly FORK_BINARY=zdpdruckuiserv_at.bin
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: process_count=0; # for checking the number of process starts
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: 	 if [[ ! -f ${BIN_PATH}/${FORK_BINARY} ]]; then
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: 		 echo "Error: Binary \"${BIN_PATH}/${FORK_BINARY}\" does not exist!" | tee -a $LOG_RESOURCE
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh:	 msg=`stop_process "${FORK_BINARY}" "-P"`
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: 	 typeset -i rc_fork=$?;
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: 	 rc=${rc}${rc_fork}
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh:	 msg=`status_process "${FORK_BINARY}"`
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: 	 typeset -i rc_fork=$?;
pharmos.base.cdm\dev\src\misc\proc\at\cdm_print_eshu.sh: 	 rc=${rc}+${rc_fork}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\oat21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\obg21\bg\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 echo "$PROCNAME: Parameter value missed or invalid value \$vz: >$vz<!" | tee -a $LOG_RESOURCE

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:	# set informix dir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:		for i in `ls ${DATA_PATH}/input/xstocklevel-*-*.info`; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:		# determine interbranchtransfer branches for customer
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "Determined the following interbranchtransfer branches for this customer:" >> ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "SELECT * FROM t${BRANCHNO} INTO TEMP tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock WITH NO LOG;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "UPDATE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock SET bestand=(SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo " tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno) WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo " (SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno); " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "SELECT * FROM t${IBTBranch} INTO TEMP tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock WITH NO LOG;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "UPDATE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock SET bestand=(SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo " tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno) WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo " (SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno); " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr AS article, " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "NVL(tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.verbundartikel, '0') AS flagibt, " >> ${SQLFILE} 
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "NVL(tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.bestand, '0') AS stockleveldc " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo ", NVL(tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.bestand, '0') AS stocklevelibt${IBTBranch}" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "FROM tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo ", OUTER tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "AND tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "DROP TABLE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "DROP TABLE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "executing query for customer ${CUSTOMER} of branch ${BRANCHNO}"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ode21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "finished query for customer ${CUSTOMER} of branch ${BRANCHNO}"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 INFORMIXDIR=${INFORMIXDIR%/*};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 export INFORMIXDIR;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_rc
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function transforming the bool value '0' and '1' to the strings 'FALSE' and 'TRUE'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_bool
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 # Creating directory for split files
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 for file in ${OUTPUTFILE_PATH}/*
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 if (( ${FALSE} == ${clearbeforeload_flag} )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:		print_debug "...skipping truncate because -clearbeforeload option was not set!"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 #set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\unload_stockweb.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\unload_stockweb.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\unload_stockweb.sh: 	 export INFORMIXDIR;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\unload_stockweb.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\unload_stockweb.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ofr21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\unload_stockweb.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ohr21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: vz=0;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: process_count=0; # for checking the number of process starts
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: readonly VZ_OPTION="-vz";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh:	 echo "\$VZ_OPTION:			>$VZ_OPTION<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh:	 echo "\$vz:			>$vz<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$VZ_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 				 vz=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 	 if [[ "$vz" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_numeric_parameter "$vz"` )) || [[ "$vz" == "0" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 echo "$PROCNAME: Parameter value missed or invalid value \$vz: >$vz<!" | tee -a $LOG_RESOURCE
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $VZ_OPTION $vz"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 _parameters="$VZ_OPTION $vz";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: #Creation-Date:     24.04.2012

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: INFORMIXDIR=${INFORMIXDIR};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # Sets the directory of informix automatically
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_rc
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function transforming the bool value '0' and '1' to the strings 'FALSE' and 'TRUE'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_bool
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\ors21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "Determined the following interbranchtransfer branches for this customer:" >> ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "SELECT * FROM t${BRANCHNO} INTO TEMP tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock WITH NO LOG;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "UPDATE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock SET bestand=(SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo " tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno) WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo " (SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno); " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "SELECT * FROM t${IBTBranch} INTO TEMP tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock WITH NO LOG;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "UPDATE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock SET bestand=(SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo " tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno) WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo " (SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno); " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 INFORMIXDIR=${INFORMIXDIR%/*};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 export INFORMIXDIR;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_rc
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function transforming the bool value '0' and '1' to the strings 'FALSE' and 'TRUE'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_bool
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 # Creating directory for split files
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 for file in ${OUTPUTFILE_PATH}/*
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 if (( ${FALSE} == ${clearbeforeload_flag} )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:		print_debug "...skipping truncate because -clearbeforeload option was not set!"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 #set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\hr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh:	 printf "%-30s%-90s\n" "\$minagefororderprotocol:" ">$minagefororderprotocol<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pat\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\pfr\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh:	 printf "%-30s%-90s\n" "\$minagefororderprotocol:" ">$minagefororderprotocol<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # Sets the directory of informix automatically
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_rc
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function transforming the bool value '0' and '1' to the strings 'FALSE' and 'TRUE'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_bool
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zdev21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: vz=0;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: process_count=0; # for checking the number of process starts
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: readonly VZ_OPTION="-vz";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh:	 echo "\$VZ_OPTION:			>$VZ_OPTION<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh:	 echo "\$vz:			>$vz<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$VZ_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 				 vz=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 	 if [[ "$vz" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_numeric_parameter "$vz"` )) || [[ "$vz" == "0" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 echo "$PROCNAME: Parameter value missed or invalid value \$vz: >$vz<!" | tee -a $LOG_RESOURCE
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $VZ_OPTION $vz"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\at\ksc\load\proc\loadconditions.sh: 		 _parameters="$VZ_OPTION $vz";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh:	 printf "%-30s%-90s\n" "\$minagefororderprotocol:" ">$minagefororderprotocol<"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderproposal=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 if [[ "$1" == "$MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 				 minagefororderprotocol=$1;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderproposal}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderproposal}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderproposal}: >${minagefororderproposal}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${minagefororderprotocol}" == "" ]] || (( 1 != `check_string_parameter "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" "${minagefororderprotocol}"` )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 echo "${PROCNAME}: Parameter value missed or invalid value \${minagefororderprotocol}: >${minagefororderprotocol}<!" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 	 if [[ "${_OPTION}" == "${MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION}" ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\ch\ksc\load\proc\cscbatchhistory.sh: 		 _parameters="${_parameters} $BRANCH_OPTION $branch $LTORDERDATE_OPTION $ltorderdate $MINAGEFORORDERPROPOSAL_OPTION $minagefororderproposal $MINAGEFORORDERPROTOCOL_OPTION $minagefororderprotocol"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "SELECT * FROM t${BRANCHNO} INTO TEMP tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock WITH NO LOG;" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "UPDATE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock SET bestand=(SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo " tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno) WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo " (SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno); " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "UPDATE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock SET bestand=(SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo " tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno) WHERE " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo " (SELECT quota FROM tquota WHERE tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tquota.articleno); " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "NVL(tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.verbundartikel, '0') AS flagibt, " >> ${SQLFILE} 
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "NVL(tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.bestand, '0') AS stockleveldc " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo ", NVL(tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.bestand, '0') AS stocklevelibt${IBTBranch}" >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			echo "FROM tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo ", OUTER tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:				echo "AND tvz${BRANCHNO}quotedstock.artikel_nr = tvz${IBTBranch}quotedstock.artikel_nr " >> ${SQLFILE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\de\ksc\load\proc\xswstocklevel.sh:			for IBTBranch in ${arrIBTBranches[*]}; do

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 printf "%-30s%-90s\n" "\$CLEARBEFORELOAD_OPTION:" ">$CLEARBEFORELOAD_OPTION<"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # Sets the directory of informix automatically
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 INFORMIXDIR=${INFORMIXDIR%/*};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 export INFORMIXDIR;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_rc
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function transforming the bool value '0' and '1' to the strings 'FALSE' and 'TRUE'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_bool
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 # Creating directory for split files
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 for file in ${OUTPUTFILE_PATH}/*
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 if (( ${FALSE} == ${clearbeforeload_flag} )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:		print_debug "...skipping truncate because -clearbeforeload option was not set!"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 #set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\fr\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # Sets the directory of informix automatically
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function set_informixdir
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="set_informixdir";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 if [[ "" == ${INFORMIXDIR} ]]; then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_rc
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # function transforming the bool value '0' and '1' to the strings 'FALSE' and 'TRUE'
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: function transform_bool
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\environment\zqas21\rs\ksc\load\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: # function function transforming the integer return code '0', '1' and '2'

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:		for i in ${ARRAY_TURNOVER_FAK[@]}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:						print_debug "...error <${errno}>, No read rights for SAP-Limit file!"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 local _FUNCNAME="format_turnover";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 # format comma to dot

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: # getting turnover + returns from database and format it
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 touch "${PATH_TURNOVER_FORMAT}"

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 print_debug "...format unloaded file OK";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: # formatting exported sap limit file
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: function format_sap_limit_file
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 local _FUNCNAME="format_sap_limit_file";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: # formatting exported sap balance file
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: function format_sap_balance_file
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 local _FUNCNAME="format_sap_balance_file";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 # format comma to dot

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	}' ${PATH_SAP_LIMIT_EXPORT_FORMAT} >> ${PATH_SAP_EXPORT_SQL}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	for i in ${ARRAY_TURNOVER_FAK[@]}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 # check if formatted sap file is existing

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:  		 errno=${RET_CODE_SAP_SQL_FORMAT_FAILED};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: Loading file into temp table failed (formatting error)!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 # check if formatted sap file is existing
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 check_is_file_existing "${PATH_SAP_BALANCE_EXPORT_FORMAT}";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:  		 errno=${RET_CODE_SAP_BALANCE_FORMAT_FILE_NOT_EXISTING};

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	}' ${PATH_FAK_EXPORT_FORMAT} >> ${PATH_FAK_EXPORT_SQL}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:  		 errno=${RET_CODE_SAP_SQL_FORMAT_FAILED};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: Formatting of SAP balance sql file failed!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 # check if formatted sap file is existing
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 check_is_file_existing "${PATH_SAP_BALANCE_EXPORT_FORMAT}";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:  		 errno=${RET_CODE_SAP_BALANCE_FORMAT_FILE_NOT_EXISTING};

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	}' ${PATH_SAP_BALANCE_EXPORT_FORMAT} >> ${PATH_SAP_EXPORT_SQL}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:  		 errno=${RET_CODE_SAP_SQL_FORMAT_FAILED};
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: Formatting of SAP balance sql file failed!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 print_debug "...format SAP limits";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 backup_file "${PATH_SAP_LIMIT_EXPORT_FORMAT}";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: function perform_crema_check_and_deletion
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 local _FUNCNAME="perform_crema_sqls";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:		 # creating sql file for deletion      #
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:						JOIN debtlevelformail dlfm ON ct.typeid = dlfm.id \
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:						JOIN amountformail afm ON ct.typeid = afm.id  \
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 cat /dev/null > ${PATH_SAP_BALANCE_EXPORT_FORMAT}; 
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:	 cat /dev/null > ${PATH_TURNOVER_FORMAT}; 
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh:		 perform_crema_check_and_deletion;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\debtlimit.sh: 	 echo "\n>Return `transform_rc ${rc}`\n...${errmsg}\n" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadpseudotours.sh: 		 errmsg="ERROR - ${_FUNCNAME}: Environment variable 'INFORMIXDIR' is empty. No modification could be made.";

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadpseudotours.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_rc";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadpseudotours.sh: 		 *) _result="No transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadpseudotours.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadpseudotours.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}

pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 local _FUNCNAME="transform_bool";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 *) _result="No bool transformation possible - no valid value passed (<_rc>)!";;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 		 errmsg="${_FUNCNAME}: No read rights for passed input file <${_INPUTFILENAME}>!";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: # evaluating input file for further usage
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 # Creating directory for split files
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 for file in ${OUTPUTFILE_PATH}/*
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:	 if (( ${FALSE} == ${clearbeforeload_flag} )); then
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh:		print_debug "...skipping truncate because -clearbeforeload option was not set!"
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 msg="${PROCNAME}: Setting the informixdir.";
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: BEGIN Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 set_informixdir;
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: "`transform_rc ${rc}` | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo " ${cnt_step}. Step: END Setting the INFORMIX specific directory." | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
pharmos.outbound.csc_load\dev\src\_scripts\proc\loadquotabyfile.sh: 	 echo "Return code: `transform_rc ${rc}`: ${errmsg}" | tee -a ${LOG_RESOURCE}
